'''Blue Jazz''' is a [[Flowers|flower]] that can be [[Crops|grown]] from [[Jazz Seeds]] in 7 days.

If placed within proper range of a [[Bee House#Range|Bee House]] (5 squares in any cardinal direction), Blue Jazz will cause [[Honey|Blue Jazz Honey]] to be produced, increasing the honey base value from {{Price|100}} to {{Price|200}}.

Blue Jazz can be purchased from the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|50}}.

