==Tailoring==
Blue Jazz can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring#Pants|Skirt]]. [[File:Skirt.png|36px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a blue dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
Blue Jazz is not used in any [[quests]].

==Notes==
*Blue Jazz has an equal chance of being one of six different colors.  Blue Jazz of different colors will occupy different slots in inventory or chests.  Six colors &times; four [[Crops#Crop Quality|quality]] levels = 24 possible spaces used.
:[[File:BlueJazzColors.png]]

